title: Highway Dragnet (1954 Richard Conte, Joan Bennett - Film Noir

sources.description: Highway Dragnet is a 1954 film noir crime film directed by Nathan Juran from a story by U.S. Anderson and Roger Corman. The film stars Richard Conte, Joan Bennett and Wanda Hendrix.
